[section#linalg.algs.blas2.rank1
    [:en] Rank-1 (outer product) update of a matrix
    [:zh_CN] 矩阵的秩-1（外积）更新
]

[para]
[:en] The following elements apply to all functions in [#linalg.algs.blas2.rank1].
[:zh_CN] 下列各元素适用于 [#linalg.algs.blas2.rank1] 中的所有函数。

[para:mandates]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[*possibly-multipliable]<OutMat, InVec2, InVec1>()] is [`true], and
[:zh_CN] [`[*possibly-multipliable]<OutMat, InVec2, InVec1>()] 为 [`true]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`[*possibly-addable]<OutMat, InMat, OutMat>()] is [`true] for those
overloads with an [`E] parameter.
[:zh_CN] [`[*possibly-addable]<OutMat, InMat, OutMat>()] 对于带有形参 [`E] 的重载为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:expects]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[*multipliable](A, y, x)] is [`true], and
[:zh_CN] [`[*multipliable](A, y, x)] 为 [`true]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`[*addable](A, E, A)] is [`true] for those overloads with an [`E] parameter.
[:zh_CN] [`[*addable](A, E, A)] 对于带有形参 [`E] 的重载为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:complexity]
[:en] [?bigoh [`x.extent(0)] \times [`y.extent(0)]].
[:zh_CN] [?bigoh [`x.extent(0)] \times [`y.extent(0)]]。

[%@lib matrix_rank_1_update]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update(InVec1 x, InVec2 y, OutMat A);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, InVec1 x, InVec2 y, OutMat A);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] These functions perform an overwriting nonsymmetric nonconjugated rank-1 update.
[:zh_CN] 这些函数实施重写的非对称非共轭的秩-1 更新。

[begin:note]
[:en] These functions correspond to the BLAS functions [`xGER] (for real element
types) and [`xGERU] (for complex element types)[#:cite@super#blas2].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数对应于 BLAS 函数 [`xGER]（对于实数元素类型）和 [`xGERU]（对于
复数元素类型）[#:cite@super#blas2]。
[end:note]

[para:effects]
[:en] Computes [$A = x y^T].
[:zh_CN] 计算 [$A = x y^T]。
[div:end]

[%@lib matrix_rank_1_update]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat, [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update(InVec1 x, InVec2 y, InMat E, OutMat A);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat,
         [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, InVec1 x, InVec2 y, InMat E, OutMat A);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] These functions perform an updating nonsymmetric nonconjugated rank-1 update.
[:zh_CN] 这些函数实施更新的非对称非共轭的秩-1 更新。

[begin:note]
[:en] These functions correspond to the BLAS functions [`xGER] (for real element
types) and [`xGERU] (for complex element types)[#:cite@super#blas2].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数对应于 BLAS 函数 [`xGER]（对于实数元素类型）和 [`xGERU]（对于
复数元素类型）[#:cite@super#blas2]。
[end:note]

[para:effects]
[:en] Computes [$A = E + x y^T].
[:zh_CN] 计算 [$A = E + x y^T]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] [`A] may alias [`E].
[:zh_CN] [`A] 可能为 [`E] 的别名。
[div:end]

[%@lib matrix_rank_1_update_c]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update_c(InVec1 x, InVec2 y, OutMat A);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update_c(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, InVec1 x, InVec2 y, OutMat A);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] These functions perform an overwriting nonsymmetric conjugated rank-1 update.
[:zh_CN] 这些函数实施覆写的非对称共轭的秩-1 更新。

[begin:note]
[:en] These functions correspond to the BLAS functions [`xGER] (for real element
types) and [`xGERC] (for complex element types)[#:cite@super#blas2].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数对应于 BLAS 函数 [`xGER]（对于实数元素类型）和 [`xGERC]（对于
复数元素类型）[#:cite@super#blas2]。
[end:note]

[para:effects]
[list]
[item]
[:en] For the overloads without an [`ExecutionPolicy] argument, equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 对于没有 [`ExecutionPolicy] 实参的重载，等价于：
[codeblock]
matrix_rank_1_update(x, conjugated(y), A);
[codeblock:end]
[item]
[:en@~] otherwise, equivalent to:
[:zh_CN@~] 否则，等价于：
[codeblock]
matrix_rank_1_update(std::forward<ExecutionPolicy>(exec), x, conjugated(y), A);
[codeblock:end]
[list:end]
[div:end]

[%@lib matrix_rank_1_update_c]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat, [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update_c(InVec1 x, InVec2 y, InMat E, OutMat A);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-vector InVec2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat,
         [[redoc("*:c>")]]out-matrix OutMat>
  void matrix_rank_1_update_c(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, InVec1 x, InVec2 y, InMat E, OutMat A);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] These functions perform an updating nonsymmetric conjugated rank-1 update.
[:zh_CN] 这些函数实施更新的非对称共轭的秩-1 更新。

[begin:note]
[:en] These functions correspond to the BLAS functions [`xGER] (for real element
types) and [`xGERC] (for complex element types)[#:cite@super#blas2].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数对应于 BLAS 函数 [`xGER]（对于实数元素类型）和 [`xGERC]（对于
复数元素类型）[#:cite@super#blas2]。
[end:note]

[para:effects]
[list]
[item]
[:en] For the overloads without an [`ExecutionPolicy] argument, equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 对于没有 [`ExecutionPolicy] 实参的重载，等价于：
[codeblock]
matrix_rank_1_update(x, conjugated(y), A);
[codeblock:end]
[item]
[:en@~] otherwise, equivalent to:
[:zh_CN@~] 否则，等价于：
[codeblock]
matrix_rank_1_update(std::forward<ExecutionPolicy>(exec), x, conjugated(y), E, A);
[codeblock:end]
[list:end]
[div:end]
